item.title: Elie Ayache
item.description: Serge graduated from ESSEC, the French business school, in 1986, before leading a long and successful banking career in Paris, London and New-York as a fixed-income specialist, for names like CCF, UBS and Credit Suisse. He gained significant experience in market-making, trading, and risk-management. Serge is a co-founder of ITO 33, and the one in charge of our business and commercial endeavors. He delights in the possibility that ITO 33 may grow to captivate the financial services community as a company with a grand vision and lofty aspirations, while being grounded in its research, engineering and hands-on spirit.
